*The small ship screamed out in protest as it entered the earths atmosphere, 
heating the ships hull to mealting point. Inside the three bots fratically 
tried to manuver the small ship into a safe position to land. They hurried 
to and fro. Trying despretly to find a safe place to crash if they couldn't 
control the plumeting ship.*

  Snow Tech mutters to all within muttering distance:
" Prepare for a crash landing ladies and gents. Please take the proper 
procedures, make shure that you are succured properly, have all lose luggage 
tied down, then bend down and kiss your ass good-bye!"

* Shadow Cat frowned towards her twin brother and smaked his arm.*

Shadow Cat:
" Don't be an ass Snow Tech, this is serious! Now find a clearing to crash 
in!"

* Snow Tech Doges the hit and smiles back at the teed off female bot, going 
to the screen, he quickly scans the local planet for a crash site. Upon 
finding one, he sets the course of their ship to the co-ordinations. Making 
shure that it did not veer off course.*
* The third bot, just a small tyke of nine, watched helplessly as the two 
grown bots tried to save their lives. He began to cry in small sobs, only to 
be gently hushed by Shadow Cat. After setting the course, the two went to 
their seats, buckling down and sucuring the little one, just in case. They 
sat back and held on, hoping for the best....*

* On Earth, a small lynx and dove played together. Oblivious to the fact 
they where enimies. A bright light up ahead made them both look up. The 
light began to fall at greater speed, passing them with a sonic boom. The 
two little forest animals, being babies, where more curious than afraid by 
this monstrous noise and flash. So, they walked towards the ship, following 
thier noses(Or beaks) in animal fashion.
They find a small ship in ruins, flashes and small explosions still kept the 
two from getting any closer. Suddenly, a yellow beam flashes outwards, 
scaring the two away, but not before they where anilized and fed into the 
ships computer.*
  * The pod door opens and a black leopard and a white leopard steps out 
followed by a small flying lynx with white wings.....*
